        protected String getBaseTypeName(com.google.gwt.core.ext.typeinfo.JClassType type)
        Returns a simple types, including classes and interfaces, parameterized, and raw types. Null is returned for other types such as arrays and type parameters (e.g., 'E' in java.util.List) because filtering is meaningless for such types.
